caption.body: Exhibition rotations are a team effort as objects are transported through the terminal to the gallery, unloaded, arranged for an assembly-line fashion of installation. Take a ride on a rack as we sail through Terminal 2 to install @SFOMuseum's most recent exhibition, The Mysterious Talking Board: #OuijaAndBeyond.  Learn more about #Ouija boards in "The Mysterious Talking Board: #OuijaAndBeyond", located post-security, in Terminal 2. http://bit.ly/OuijaAndBeyond  G O O D B Y E
